description: Avricore Health Inc. engages in the health data and point-of-care technologies business in Canada. It provides HealthTab, a lab-accurate point of care testing platform for pharmacy. The company has strategic partnerships with Shoppers Drug Marts and Abbott. The company was formerly known as Vanc Pharmaceuticals Inc. and changed its name to Avricore Health Inc. in October 2018. Avricore Health Inc. was founded in 1996 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
